e":{"pid":"2eef205f97dbd3c84affcd8e15d9dfe549d39998","tid":2170911,"uid":305548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:59:57.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪轉到三寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T17:50:00.000Z","msg":"太少人咁玩法,唔想比人起底,<br />\nU downgrade左但科upgrade左<br />\n我就覺得u 唔重要,讀邊科先重要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T17:52:49.000Z","msg":"巴打UGC tran UGC？<br />\n點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGPA好高？interview表現好好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T17:58:17.000Z","msg":"係UGC 轉UGC,所以要行non jupas 自己入紙去個別大學<br />\n我係轉埋field,連year 1考試都冇考, 亦冇interview"},{"pid":"2e4f30044e9848e1d9bd97c19451cb767cde3abb","tid":2170911,"uid":301923,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:00:57.000Z","msg":"你覺得值得咪考多年囉<br />\n你想做既就唔應該理人地點反對<br />\n畀你讀咗科唔中意/乞食科<br />\n過咗四年之後你只會後悔當初冇retake<br />\n與其會後悔 你想考既不如考多年<br />\n屋企唔係等你開飯就唔使擔心咁多<br />\n無乜顧慮嘅時候不如趁青春有本錢嗰陣考多次<br />\n唔得咪接受現實 Asso/hd or入返u<br />\n得咗咪開香檳囉<br />\n起碼都叫嘗試過<br />\n你唔使聽人講咩遲讀一年揾小十幾萬呢啲廢話<br />\n你唔博嘅話遲下冇多幾百萬 甚至幾千萬"},{"pid":"5ab2406741aeacf84343f3ef50b87c54341def31","tid":2170911,"uid":16859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c1e7f96264a901c4cbe781207d2bfecbec47b2d7","tid":2170911,"uid":117386,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T17:03:31.000Z","msg":"呢個時代讀乜都乞食嫁啦<br />\n唔好浪費青春啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T19:07:16.000Z","msg":"this is gold"},{"pid":"99ed37f8823931d0f5ae79b00278adce1c1f8523","tid":2170911,"uid":358248,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T19:22:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac951cfd173d869f5a9064d5cfd79eae3263aabe","tid":2170911,"uid":172506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T22:27:12.000Z","msg":"既然本身你已經有呢個諗法 我會勸你 去！<br />\n始終差少少<br />\n做咗 唔得 好過你呢一世都後悔無做<br />\n本身成績又唔係差 一兩年時間真係唔奢侈<br />\n今年都有位人兄 23歲個時返住工去讀夜校由中4讀起<br />\n今年25歲先第一次dse 最後入咗poly3寶<br />\n但你應承自己呢次係最後一次<br />\n下年都係fail就認命啦"},{"pid":"c99c01b4fff667ae137596fccadb29e08849ccd9","tid":2170911,"uid":213846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cea59d349d7c2189c71cd176b78fd188bddb0374","tid":2170911,"uid":305548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T14:51:06.000Z","msg":"小弟今年係dse retaker，aim入三寶，不過都係爭啲入唔到，最後入咗bme，但係聽人講讀bme會乞食<br />\n想問吓如果唔講興趣，淨係講錢嘅話好唔好用多一年時間考多次dse搏入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T23:42:46.000Z","msg":"如果覺得唔考多次會成世後悔<br />\n就去考多次<br />\n如果屋企唔係等你開飯，番少一兩年工對你番工人生嚟講，絕對唔係問題<br />\n到時番番下你仲想唔做添！"},{"pid":"65714cb258774751cd86cdd3303bcd653f1e6c8d","tid":2170911,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T23:56:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"313ce2b73edf283c7b18e5f0d9a6df24f97d3cde","tid":2170911,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T23:57:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52267ce77764f2d4b1c006489924ad4cb0be2545","tid":2170911,"uid":205272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"57c29c887977d2fcd526f562db0f807d214713eb","tid":2170911,"uid":305548,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d785faac0fc7a209e333a1e77c5860d92305de6","tid":2170911,"uid":369321,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"我雖然唔熟poly同bme/三寶，但係我諗你要講下自己幾分同差幾多，d巴打先幫到你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T15:07:38.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2019:<br />\n345(3)4554(bio chem bafs)<br />\n2020:<br />\n555(3)4655(bio chem bafs)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T00:29:27.000Z","msg":"我學校有師兄triple 讀埋土 物理治療<br />\nAL:<br />\n2005: 唔夠分，衰英文<br />\n2006: AL 理科3條C 衰英文<br />\n2007: 得左<br />\n共勉之"},{